probably find more creepy shit.

00:04:01.340 --> 00:04:02.340
And who on Earth accepts a friend request
from someone like this without some extra

00:04:02.340 --> 00:04:03.340
investigation.

00:04:03.340 --> 00:04:07.760
I’d definitely at least Google her to see
if she shows up on Murderpedia or something.

00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:12.440
She’s not using her real name, Ma Rina,
which is odd as well.

00:04:12.440 --> 00:04:16.760
There is literally no online information about
this creepy girl who wants to be our friend

00:04:16.760 --> 00:04:18.000
out of the blue.

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:20.370
Red flags are popping up everywhere.

00:04:20.370 --> 00:04:25.010
Marina also has trichotillomania, which is
a mental illness.

00:04:25.010 --> 00:04:30.000
