00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:35.120
to seek relief from emotional distress, not
some advanced OCD.

00:04:35.120 --> 00:04:40.380
It should be pretty obvious that she’s damaged,
probably suicidal, and obviously is lonely

00:04:40.380 --> 00:04:44.060
