The spelling of magick is interesting though,
as the k at the end is used to differentiate

00:05:05.430 --> 00:05:10.530
it as occult magick, not some David Blaine
shit.

00:05:10.530 --> 00:05:17.100
That’s a bit weird.

00:05:17.100 --> 00:05:22.210
Hymenopterology, which is the study of wasps,
