00:06:30.110 --> 00:06:34.710
Now, there’s a chance that she’d fixate
on us and continue pressing us to be friends.

00:06:34.710 --> 00:06:37.230
How should we handle this?

00:06:37.230 --> 00:06:40.190
We need to ignore all her online messages.

00:06:40.190 --> 00:06:45.000
If she confronts us in person asking if we
want to be friends, we’ll politely but firmly

00:06:45.000 --> 00:06:46.010
decline.

00:06:46.010 --> 00:06:50.560
If she doesn’t give up after we declined
all her previous advances, it’s pretty clear

00:06:50.560 --> 00:06:52.790
we have a stalker on our hands.

00:06:52.790 --> 00:06:57.460
According to Google, one of the most important
things to do at this point is to not engage

00:06:57.460 --> 00:06:59.090
them at all.

00:06:59.090 --> 00:07:04.230
Stalkers will typically misconstrue any contact
or interaction as validation of a relationship

00:07:04.230 --> 00:07:05.389
between us.

00:07:05.389 --> 00:07:10.030
We don’t want to make threats or jump straight
into obtaining a restraining order, this may

00:07:10.030 --> 00:07:13.230
just infuriate them and cause them to get
violent.

00:07:13.230 --> 00:07:18.450
Besides that, we need to document everything
that happens, stay vigilant, make sure our

00:07:18.450 --> 00:07:23.190
home is locked up at night, and probably buy
some mace for good measure.

00:07:23.190 --> 00:07:28.420
In California, which is where Laura is going
to college, stalking is defined as any person

00:07:28.420 --> 00:07:34.141
who willfully, maliciously, and repeatedly
follows or harasses another person and who

00:07:34.141 --> 00:07:38.860
makes a credible threat with the intent to
place that person in reasonable fear for his

00:07:38.860 --> 00:07:42.780
or her safety, or the safety of his or her
immediate family.

00:07:42.780 --> 00:07:48.330
If weeks pass and Marina hasn’t moved, and
instead has gotten more aggressive, elevate

00:07:48.330 --> 00:07:50.280
the situation to the police.

00:07:50.280 --> 00:07:54.800
You’ll likely be able to get her charged
with stalking with the evidence you’ve accrued

00:07:54.800 --> 00:07:56.720
documenting all your encounters.

00:07:56.720 --> 00:08:02.070
According to mental-illness-policy.org, if
someone is considered to be imminently dangerous

00:08:02.070 --> 00:08:07.419
