admitted to a psychiatric hospital.

00:08:07.419 --> 00:08:13.110
In the movie we later see that she’s already
been diagnosed with psychosis, reactive attachment

00:08:13.110 --> 00:08:15.730
disorder, and trichotillomania.

00:08:15.730 --> 00:08:20.000
Considering these illnesses will be discovered
